{"tid":1810219,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"上市無限期押後   小米 MIX Alpha 無疾而終好核突","createTime":"2020-01-03T16:32:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T17:27:55.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a164344f1816dc06ff3719aa13d8fbd633efac86","tid":1810219,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T16:32:01.000Z","msg":"去年 9 月小米發表了造型相當前衛的 MIX Alpha ，除了三鏡頭相機以外，整部機身都被柔性屏幕包圍覆蓋。這部擁有 1.08 億像素相機、180.6 屏佔比的MIX Alpha，小米表示零售價高達 19,999 人民幣（折合 HK$22,369），小米 MIX Alpha 在 12 月曾經於天貓和官網短暫上架，但消費者當時無法按鍵購買。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2020-01/03/214875/uniqlo_1_37e29176512ce2ac4feaa4daf8c0b9a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2020-01%2F03%2F214875%2Funiqlo_1_37e29176512ce2ac4feaa4daf8c0b9a7.jpg&h=e484f0dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小米 CEO 雷軍在去年 9 月曾經表示，小米 MIX Alpha 以屏幕包圍機身的生產技術相當複雜，所以不會大量投產，而是會以限量方式銷售，<span style=\"color: red;\">似乎他們低估了生產難度</span>，MIX Alpha很大機會無疾而終收場。根據網站《Abacus News》的報導，小米已經決定押後推出 MIX Alpha，而且沒有給予上市的日期，只表示有新的消息會再另行公佈。多間外國傳媒嘗試向小米進一步了解，但都未獲回覆。"},{"pid":"896cc64f05b480033394ce183496ce22b67f1dd3","tid":1810219,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T16:32:30.000Z","msg":"綜合大陸和外國傳媒對此事的看法，他們的理解相當一致，就是小米 MIX Alpha 已經無限期押後，而胎死腹中的機會相當高。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4568/214875/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4568%2F214875%2F1%2F&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDuTO5ApsLFANoEfWU0iq%2Bkc%3D&h=b052d7a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4568/214875/1/</a>"},{"pid":"221e58c7a4810aac4278f918fdb0579a23bb3367","tid":1810219,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T16:38:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab20244e81e2aa5c7469c3968dd450fc814b59b2","tid":1810219,"uid":159448,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"cite